 This is a list of people associated with the modern Russian Federation, the
 Soviet Union, Imperial Russia, Russian Tsardom, the Grand Duchy of Moscow, and
 other predecessor states of Russia.

Regardless of ethnicity or emigration, the list includes famous natives of
Russia and its predecessor states, as well as people who were born elsewhere
but spent most of their active life in Russia. For more information, see the
articles Russians and Demographics of Russia. For specific lists of
Russians, see and .
